<voice_0x01000ABD><se_low>Quartermaster: Prepare to set sail!
Weigh anchor!
<voice_0x01000ABE><se_low>*: Ooh, I hates this, Tenta!

<voice_0x01000ABF><se_low>*: I hates it too, Tickles!
These nasty humans and their ships,
always sailin' over poor Khalamari's head!

<voice_0x01000AC0><se_low>Khalamari: Yeah, Tenta, yeah!
Humans don't have no manners!
<voice_0x01000AC1><se_low>Khalamari: That's right, Tickles, they don't have none at all, they don't! No!

<voice_0x01000AC2><se_low>Khalamari: That's why Khalamari's gonna stand up
for all the poor creatures of the sea!
Starting by eatin' these here humans!

<voice_0x01000AC3><se_low>Khalamari: Yeah, Tickles!
He'll eat 'em! Eat 'em right up!
<voice_0x01000AC7><se_low>Khalamari: What, you again? Humans don't know when to give it a rest, do they, Tickles?

<voice_0x01000AC1><se_low>Khalamari: Yeah, Tenta, yeah! Yeah baby!
They don't know when to call it a day!
<voice_0x01000AC8><se_low>Khalamari: Well, they're in for a beatin' now, Tickles, they are! They won't be coming back again, they won't!

<voice_0x01000AC9><se_low>Khalamari: No, they won't, Tenta!
No, they won't be coming back at all!

<voice_0x01000ACA><se_low>Khalamari: Oog, they was stronger than we thought.
We give up, we give up!

<voice_0x01000ACB><se_low>Khalamari: It wasn't our fault, though!
It was HIS! That's right, it was!
<voice_0x01000ACC><se_low>Khalamari: That jester, he came walkin' on top of the water to us! Just walked over us, he did!
<voice_0x01000ACD><se_low>Khalamari: Pretty cheeky of a human to pull that little trick off, we thought, so we talked to him, we did!
<voice_0x01000ACE><se_low>Khalamari: But when he talked, our head got all cloudy-like and we started attackin' ships, we did, we did!

<voice_0x01000ACF><se_low>Khalamari: It wasn't us, it was that jester, it was!
Here's this by way of an apology, like. Ooh...

<voice_0x01000AD0><se_low>Khalamari: We found it in the ocean, we did.
Go on, take it, mate!
It's the least we can do, it is, it is.
<Cap><leader> receives <INDEF_ART_SGL_I_NAME_1> and puts <IF_PLR_NOUN_I_NAME_1>them<ELSE_NOT_PLR_NOUN_I_NAME_1>it<ENDIF_PLR_NOUN_I_NAME_1> in the bag.

<voice_0x01000AD1><se_low>Khalamari: Well, that is all from us.
We are leavin' now, we are.
Have a pleasant trip! So long!

<voice_0x01000AD2><se_high>Jessica: Not bad, guys!
You're a lot stronger than you look!
<voice_0x01000AD3><se_high>Jessica: You know, we've never properly introduced ourselves. I'm Jessica. Jessica Albert.
<voice_0x01000AD4><se_high>Jessica: And who might you be?

<voice_0x01000AD5><se_low>Yangus: I'm Yangus.
And <hero> 'ere's the guv!

<voice_0x01000AD6><se_high>Jessica: Yangus and the guv, is it? Right.
Thanks again for your help with the sea monster. Now, let's find Dhoulmagus!

<voice_0x01000AD7><se_high>Jessica: I'm sure you need to get ready first,
so let's head back to Port Prospect.
I'll tell the captain to weigh anchor.
<voice_0x01000AD8><se_high>Jessica: Oh! I almost forgot!

<voice_0x01000AD9><se_high>Jessica: I called you two thieves back at the tower,
and I never formally apologised. So...
<voice_0x01000ADA><se_high>Jessica: Forgive me!
<voice_0x01000ADB><se_high>Jessica: Anyway. I'll talk to the captain!

<voice_0x01000ADC><se_def>Quartermaster: All hands on deck!
Weigh anchor and prepare to come about!
We're heading back to Port Prospect!
